    {
        "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522621",
        "quote": "I think legislation needs to put an end to doctors profiting on businesses to which they can funnel patients - that is business, not medicine. If you try to call it medicine, then it is corruption. Without legislation, it will keep happening.",
