    {
        "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522638",
        "quote": "We have the sense that medical students come to medicine with a great capacity to understand the suffering of patients. And then by the end of the third year they completely lose that ability, partly because we teach them the specialized language of medicine.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Abraham Verghese",
            "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522638"
