    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522639",
        "quote": "The flip side of suicide is that it leaves a lingering question in the minds of the people who survived. It's like a cancer that's metastasized. The suicide is the cancer and the metastasis is all these people saying, Why? Why? Why?",
        "author": {
            "name": "Abraham Verghese",
            "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522639"
