    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522641",
        "quote": "I'm the first to admit that the resolution of a hand feeling the belly doesn't compare with the resolution of a CAT scan scanning the belly, but only my hand can say that it hurts at this spot and not at this spot. Only my hand can say that.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Abraham Verghese",
            "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522641"
