    {
        "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522643",
        "quote": "We're now able to show that the words of comfort trigger biological reactions which are the very things that you want, and you can use drugs to get there, or you can use words of comfort to get there, which would make your drugs so much more effective.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Abraham Verghese",
            "url": "/quotes/abraham_verghese_522643"
